{
  "stem": "895.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They said, we know everything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We're the most-- Yiddish.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were all Polish people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There weren't many from Western Europe.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There was the Dutch and some from Belgium, from Greece.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They didn't speak Yiddish.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In German.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I understand German very good.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I learned it in the camp, you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it's not similar with the Dutch language.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But there are some words, you think it-- but my wife doesn't understand a word of German.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I-- I'm good in language.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I do the crossword puzzles in four languages.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the camp, there was not much to talk about.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We was only thinking of food, trying to get some food to eat because the people were dying, getting thinner and thinner and thinner.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then it was the end.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the only thing to be alive, you got to-- had to steal.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I'm sorry.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You had to steal.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "From the packages from the Hungarians-- what they brought in, we took it out there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "If you were caught, you were finished.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So thank god I was never caught.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And my friend, Max Alderwereld, I gave you the address.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He brought in a lot of food.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He helps with a lot.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we cooked in the back of the barracks when we were in the, the night shift.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And that's how we tried it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And then all of a sudden, in September of 1944, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] in came the-- oh, a lot of SS came in the [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They said, raus!",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Raus!",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Raus!",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And there we have to stand with a German with a machine gun standing there-- in 1944.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "There was sabotage done by a few women on the crematorium to blow up the crematorium.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And we're standing there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I'm standing next to Max.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
